---
title: Creamy Peppercorn Sauce Pork with Potato Mash and Greens
description: Keep your head in the clouds with super fluffy mashed potatoes and a heavenly creamy peppercorn sauce that provide the perfect accompaniment to delicious pork loin steaks.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5b721a1eae08b551706d04a3-86a602ee.jpg
